snippet.title: CNC Gameplay Trailer #1 - Cattle and Crops - Farming Simulation 🚜🐂🌾
snippet.description:
Early Access in March 2017 - Support the development and register for Early Access:
http://www.cattleandcrops.com/kickstarter
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

We're very proud to present our official ingame gameplay trailer.

At the same time, we're launching a Kickstarter campaign with lots and lots of information.
You like what you've seen so far? 
Take your chance and grab your account for the early access in march 2017.
